00:13:08,037 --> 00:13:11,248
[girls crying]

261
00:13:11,332 --> 00:13:12,708
- [Beth grunts]
- It's you!

262
00:13:12,791 --> 00:13:14,668
[Beth, Mel groaning]

263
00:13:15,127 --> 00:13:17,004
[Erica grunting]

264
00:13:17,963 --> 00:13:19,507
- [Edward grunts]
- [body thuds]

265
00:13:19,590 --> 00:13:20,549
- [Edward grunts]
- [knife slashes]

266
00:13:20,633 --> 00:13:22,676
- [Erica groans]
- [dramatic music continues]

267
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:23,677
Erica!

268
00:13:25,012 --> 00:13:26,055
Don't!

269
00:13:26,138 --> 00:13:27,139
- Don't!
- Don't!

270
00:13:27,223 --> 00:13:29,350
Don't! Don't hurt her!

271
00:13:29,850 --> 00:13:31,101
Move!

272
00:13:31,185 --> 00:13:32,186
Get out of there!

273
00:13:32,895 --> 00:13:34,939
[sobbing] Uncle Edward, please stop!

274
00:13:35,314 --> 00:13:37,107
Don't commit any more crimes!

275
00:13:37,191 --> 00:13:39,318
[music becomes unsettling]

276
00:13:39,401 --> 00:13:41,403
You killed Louisa, didn't you?!

277
00:13:42,947 --> 00:13:46,075
[cries] I could never forget
the scar on your back!

278
00:13:46,867 --> 00:13:48,327
It was you!

279
00:13:50,246 --> 00:13:51,705
But why?

280
00:13:51,789 --> 00:13:54,708
[crying] Louisa loved you.

281
00:13:55,876 --> 00:13:58,295
We treated you like a father!

282
00:13:58,379 --> 00:14:00,339
How could you do that?!

283
00:14:00,422 --> 00:14:05,594
[unsettling music continues]

284
00:14:08,722 --> 00:14:11,350
Did she find out, too? You pig!

285
00:14:13,185 --> 00:14:14,395
What did I tell you?

286
00:14:15,354 --> 00:14:17,356
You're too damn nosy!

287
00:14:18,857 --> 00:14:20,359
That little friend of yours…

288
00:14:21,569 --> 00:14:24,655
- just appeared out of nowhere.
- [music fades]

289
00:14:24,738 --> 00:14:26,156
<i>What if,</i>

290
00:14:26,574 --> 00:14:28,117
<i>I like someone</i>

291
00:14:28,534 --> 00:14:30,369
<i>but I'm not sure if they like me too?</i>

292
00:14:31,245 --> 00:14:32,496
<i>It's simple.</i>

293
00:14:32,580 --> 00:14:33,789
<i>Just ask them.</i>

294
00:14:35,207 --> 00:14:36,375
<i>The thing is…</i>

295
00:14:37,585 --> 00:14:41,505
[pensive music playing]

296
00:14:41,589 --> 00:14:43,007
…<i>it's complicated.</i>

297
00:14:44,550 --> 00:14:46,051
<i>Is it complicated or</i>

298
00:14:46,552 --> 00:14:47,887
<i>you're just scared to hear the answer?</i>

299
00:14:50,764 --> 00:14:53,726
<i>These are the kinds of</i>
<i>things I'll surely take to heart.</i>

300
00:14:55,185 --> 00:14:56,604
<i>This person is really important, huh?</i>

301
00:14:58,314 --> 00:14:59,398
[tongue clicks] <i>Come here.</i>

302
00:15:00,149 --> 00:15:01,692
<i>I know you can do it.</i>

303
00:15:01,775 --> 00:15:04,320
<i>You've been</i>
<i>courageous with everything you do.</i>

304
00:15:04,403 --> 00:15:07,531
<i>I'm sure for that matter,</i>
<i>you'll find courage here too.</i>

305
00:15:08,282 --> 00:15:09,491
<i>I never doubted you.</i>

306
00:15:11,118 --> 00:15:12,494
<i>- Hi, Auntie!</i>
<i>- Hi, Auntie!</i>

307
00:15:12,578 --> 00:15:13,454
<i>- Hello!</i>
<i>- Good afternoon.</i>

308
00:15:13,537 --> 00:15:14,872
<i>Come in.</i>

309
00:15:16,332 --> 00:15:20,085
<i>My dad asked</i>
<i>your Uncle Edward to do something.</i>

310
00:15:23,213 --> 00:15:24,673
<i>He's not been home since yesterday.</i>

311
00:15:25,424 --> 00:15:26,467
<i>But…</i>

312
00:15:28,677 --> 00:15:30,304
<i>he'll be back soon.</i>

313
00:15:30,387 --> 00:15:33,098
<i>You should rest, Auntie. We got this.</i>

314
00:15:33,182 --> 00:15:34,725
<i>Is there anything you need?</i>

315
00:15:37,728 --> 00:15:39,521
<i>Oh, dear,</i>

316
00:15:39,605 --> 00:15:42,316
<i>can you get my medicine from my room?</i>

317
00:15:42,775 --> 00:15:45,402
<i>It's on the bedside</i>
<i>table next to my water.</i>

318
00:15:45,486 --> 00:15:47,488
<i>- Okay.</i>
<i>- Let me get it. I got it.</i>

319
00:15:48,322 --> 00:15:49,907
<i>- How are you feeling?</i>
- [footsteps retreating]

320
00:15:50,240 --> 00:15:51,742
[Mel] <i>Do you need anything else?</i>

321
00:15:51,825 --> 00:15:53,160
[unsettling music playing]

322
00:15:53,243 --> 00:15:54,370
[Christina] <i>I'm okay.</i>

323
00:15:54,453 --> 00:15:55,704
<i>Go on.</i>

324
00:15:55,788 --> 00:15:58,332
<i>- Head out to the balcony.</i>
- [Alice] <i>Okay.</i>

325
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:00,626
<i>Come on.</i>

326
00:16:01,293 --> 00:16:02,336
<i>Not in there!</i>

327
00:16:05,965 --> 00:16:08,008
<i>That's your Uncle Edward's.</i>

328
00:16:08,092 --> 00:16:09,593
<i>That's his room.</i>

329
00:16:10,177 --> 00:16:12,680
<i>He doesn't want anyone going in there.</i>

330
00:16:13,472 --> 00:16:14,765
<i>Hmm.</i>

331
00:16:15,975 --> 00:16:18,394
<i>Why, Auntie? What's Uncle hiding there?</i>

332
00:16:19,728 --> 00:16:23,399
<i>There are things from</i>
<i>the charismatic stored in there.</i>

333
00:16:23,482 --> 00:16:26,068
<i>He doesn't want them touched by anyone.</i>

334
00:16:26,652 --> 00:16:29,154
<i>Hmm. </i>[tongue clicks] <i>Okay.</i>

335
00:16:29,863 --> 00:16:31,198
[Louisa grunts softly]

336
00:16:32,366 --> 00:16:33,367
<i>Sweetheart?</i>

337
00:16:34,493 --> 00:16:35,536
<i>Sweetheart?</i>

338
00:16:36,537 --> 00:16:38,247
<i>- Hi, Uncle!</i>
<i>- Oh, you're here.</i>

339
00:16:38,330 --> 00:16:40,082
<i>Great timing. I bought banana rolls.</i>

340
00:16:40,165 --> 00:16:42,459
<i>You know exactly</i>
<i>what we like, Uncle Edward!</i>

341
00:16:42,543 --> 00:16:43,585
<i>Of course!</i>

342
00:16:43,669 --> 00:16:49,383
<i>You practically eat here every day.</i>

343
00:16:49,466 --> 00:16:52,845
<i>Besides, I wanted to cheer Louisa up.</i>

344
00:16:54,263 --> 00:16:55,597
<i>Is something wrong, Louisa?</i>

345
00:16:56,890 --> 00:16:58,225
<i>Huh?</i>

346
00:16:58,600 --> 00:16:59,560
<i>Are you okay?</i>

347
00:16:59,643 --> 00:17:02,521
[unsettling music continues]

348
00:17:02,604 --> 00:17:03,522
[Edward chuckles]

349
00:17:03,605 --> 00:17:04,565
<i>Just kidding!</i>

350
00:17:04,648 --> 00:17:07,317
<i>Louisa's fine, right?</i>

351
00:17:07,401 --> 00:17:08,485
[forced chuckles]

352
00:17:08,569 --> 00:17:10,362
<i>- Uh, I'll take those, Uncle.</i>
<i>- Oh.</i>

353
00:17:10,446 --> 00:17:12,948
<i>It's time for</i>
<i>your aunt to take her medicine.</i>

354
00:17:13,032 --> 00:17:13,824
<i>- Excuse me.</i>
<i>- Alright.</i>

355
00:17:13,907 --> 00:17:14,825
<i>I'll get her water.</i>

356
00:17:14,908 --> 00:17:16,577
<i>Okay, okay. Thank you.</i>

357
00:17:16,660 --> 00:17:18,287
<i>- It smells so good!</i>
<i>- You ready?</i>

358
00:17:18,370 --> 00:17:19,955
<i>Looks yummy!</i>

359
00:17:21,749 --> 00:17:23,751
[sinister music playing]

360
00:17:23,834 --> 00:17:25,294
[Christina] <i>Come on, heart.</i>

361
00:17:31,759 --> 00:17:33,927
<i>I'm just making</i>
<i>you some juice, sweetheart.</i>

362
00:17:34,011 --> 00:17:40,142
[sinister music continues]

363
00:17:40,225 --> 00:17:42,352
<i>Here you go, sweetheart.</i>

364
00:17:42,436 --> 00:17:43,520
[Christine chuckles softly]

365
00:17:43,604 --> 00:17:45,606
<i>Thank you, sweetheart.</i>

366
00:17:48,692 --> 00:17:50,652
[Edward] <i>I'd formed a habit.</i>

367
00:17:50,736 --> 00:17:51,737
<i>Is it good?</i>

368
00:17:51,820 --> 00:17:53,238
<i>- It's good.</i>
- [Edward chuckles]

369
00:17:53,322 --> 00:17:54,364
<i>Thank you.</i>

370
00:17:57,785 --> 00:17:59,995
[Christina] <i>I'm sorry, heart.</i>

371
00:18:00,412 --> 00:18:02,790
<i>I feel so sleepy all of the sudden.</i>

372
00:18:03,499 --> 00:18:05,626
[Edward chuckles] <i>Oh, heart, what?</i>

373
00:18:06,251 --> 00:18:08,087
<i>I've been carrying you around</i>

374
00:18:08,170 --> 00:18:10,464
<i>and taking of care of you for years.</i>

375
00:18:11,590 --> 00:18:13,592
<i>Do you not regret your choice?</i>

376
00:18:15,052 --> 00:18:17,971
<i>Your married someone with a heart disease.</i>

377
00:18:18,055 --> 00:18:20,099
<i>You heart may be ill,</i>

378
00:18:21,725 --> 00:18:26,021
<i>but you fill my heart with so much love.</i>

379
00:18:26,772 --> 00:18:27,856
[both chuckle]

380
00:18:27,940 --> 00:18:31,318
<i>I am so lucky I married you.</i>

381
00:18:34,446 --> 00:18:36,532
<i>Because I love you so much.</i>

382
00:18:36,615 --> 00:18:40,786
[pensive music playing]

383
00:18:47,251 --> 00:18:52,714
[music turns sinister]

384
00:18:56,051 --> 00:18:57,594
[girl sobbing]

385
00:18:57,678 --> 00:18:59,513
<i>Help!</i>

386
00:18:59,596 --> 00:19:05,185
[sinister music continues]

387
00:19:12,442 --> 00:19:13,777
[keys jingle]

388
00:19:19,491 --> 00:19:25,080
[sinister music continues]

389
00:19:35,799 --> 00:19:40,596
[sinister music continues]

390
00:19:52,482 --> 00:19:56,403
[music becomes foreboding]

391
00:19:56,486 --> 00:19:58,947
[girl sobbing on video]

392
00:19:59,031 --> 00:20:02,159
<i>Have mercy on me!</i>

393
00:20:02,242 --> 00:20:04,828
[sobbing continues]

394
00:20:04,912 --> 00:20:07,122
<i>- Help me!</i>
- [foreboding music crescendos]

395
00:20:07,206 --> 00:20:08,373
[Louisa] <i>Uncle!</i>

396
00:20:08,457 --> 00:20:10,167
<i>Uncle! Uncle!</i>

397
00:20:10,250 --> 00:20:11,668
<i>Hey, what's wrong?</i>

398
00:20:11,752 --> 00:20:13,003
<i>You're yelling like there's a fire.</i>

399
00:20:13,879 --> 00:20:17,549
<i>Uncle, I don't want to ask,</i>

400
00:20:18,258 --> 00:20:20,093
<i>but I have no other choice.</i>

401
00:20:20,552 --> 00:20:22,721
<i>Can I borrow 10,000 pesos?</i>

402
00:20:22,804 --> 00:20:24,223
<i>I really need it.</i>

403
00:20:25,307 --> 00:20:26,642
<i>Why? What's wrong?</i>

404
00:20:27,309 --> 00:20:28,518
<i>Maybe I can help.</i>

405
00:20:29,478 --> 00:20:30,771
<i>There's no problem,</i>

406
00:20:30,854 --> 00:20:32,731
<i>I just really need the money.</i>

407
00:20:32,814 --> 00:20:34,316
<i>I promise to pay</i>
<i>you back as soon as I can.</i>

408
00:20:34,399 --> 00:20:36,652
[Edward] <i>Maybe she was</i>
<i>going to use the money for Liezel.</i>

409
00:20:36,735 --> 00:20:38,695
<i>So they could get out of Amurao</i>

410
00:20:38,779 --> 00:20:40,405
<i>and start a new life together.</i>

411
00:20:40,489 --> 00:20:41,406
<i>When do you need it?</i>

412
00:20:41,490 --> 00:20:43,408
[uneasy music playing]

413
00:20:43,492 --> 00:20:44,701
<i>Really, Uncle?</i>

414
00:20:44,785 --> 00:20:46,703
<i>You're really going to lend me the money?!</i>

415
00:20:46,787 --> 00:20:48,455
[chuckles] <i>You said you need it!</i>

416
00:20:48,538 --> 00:20:50,624
<i>Yes! Oh, thank you, Uncle!</i>

417
00:20:50,707 --> 00:20:52,960
<i>Oh! I don't know how</i>
<i>I can make it up to you!</i>

418
00:20:53,043 --> 00:20:55,254
<i>Thank you!</i>
<i>Thank you! Thank you! Thank you!</i>

419
00:20:55,337 --> 00:20:56,672
[both chuckle]

420
00:20:56,755 --> 00:20:57,631
<i>But you sure you're okay?</i>

421
00:20:57,714 --> 00:20:59,508
<i>Yes, Uncle. I’m super duper okay!</i>

422
00:20:59,591 --> 00:21:00,801
<i>Oh, you made me so happy, Uncle!</i>

423
00:21:00,884 --> 00:21:02,678
- [Louisa giggles]
<i>- Mm, I got you.</i>

424
00:21:02,761 --> 00:21:04,179
[Edward] <i>That night, however,</i>

425
00:21:04,263 --> 00:21:06,682
<i>things did not turn out as expected.</i>

426
00:21:06,765 --> 00:21:08,684
<i>Liezel, what's the matter?</i>

427
00:21:08,767 --> 00:21:10,143
<i>Did your dad find out?</i>

428
00:21:10,227 --> 00:21:11,728
<i>Did he threaten you?</i>

429
00:21:11,812 --> 00:21:13,438
<i>Liezel, I thought you loved me?</i>

430
00:21:14,856 --> 00:21:16,358
[young Liezel]<i> I do love you.</i>

431
00:21:16,441 --> 00:21:19,695
<i>But how will I be able</i>
<i>to ignore the way people will look at me?</i>

432
00:21:20,320 --> 00:21:22,572
<i>They will judge me every single day</i>

433
00:21:22,656 --> 00:21:24,324
<i>if I choose to be with you.</i>

434
00:21:25,367 --> 00:21:26,368
[Michelle] <i>You flirt!</i>

435
00:21:26,451 --> 00:21:27,452
- [blow lands]
- [grunts]

436
00:21:27,536 --> 00:21:29,496
<i>You are just like your slut mother!</i>

437
00:21:29,579 --> 00:21:32,457
<i>Not so tough anymore, huh?</i>

438
00:21:33,375 --> 00:21:34,251
<i>Let me go!</i>

439
00:21:35,711 --> 00:21:36,586
<i>Let go!</i>

440
00:21:36,670 --> 00:21:41,591
[ominous music playing]

441
00:21:41,675 --> 00:21:42,759
[Louisa] <i>Uncle!</i>

442
00:21:43,218 --> 00:21:44,761
[panting]

443
00:21:44,845 --> 00:21:46,013
<i>Uncle?!</i>

444
00:21:46,096 --> 00:21:47,472
<i>Uncle Edward?!</i>

445
00:21:48,390 --> 00:21:50,309
[tapping]

446
00:21:50,392 --> 00:21:54,938
[ominous music continues]

447
00:21:59,943 --> 00:22:00,986
<i>Uncle?</i>

448
00:22:05,699 --> 00:22:06,700
<i>Uncle?</i>

449
00:22:06,783 --> 00:22:08,618
[music fades]

450
00:22:09,286 --> 00:22:10,370
<i>Uncle?</i>

451
00:22:10,454 --> 00:22:13,915
[breathing heavily]

452
00:22:15,334 --> 00:22:16,793
<i>Uncle Edward?</i>

453
00:22:18,086 --> 00:22:20,881
[breathes heavily]

454
00:22:31,683 --> 00:22:38,523
[unsettling music playing]

455
00:22:50,827 --> 00:22:53,413
[thunder claps]

456
00:22:53,497 --> 00:22:58,335
[unsettling music continues]

457
00:23:10,263 --> 00:23:13,391
[girl sobbing on video]
<i>Please, don't hurt me!</i>

458
00:23:13,725 --> 00:23:14,810
[Edward on video] <i>Shut up!</i>

459
00:23:15,435 --> 00:23:16,686
<i>Be quiet!</i>

460
00:23:19,689 --> 00:23:21,399
[girl continues sobbing]

461
00:23:21,483 --> 00:23:24,236
<i>- Mama!</i>
- [thunder claps]

462
00:23:24,319 --> 00:23:26,655
[sobbing continues]

463
00:23:26,738 --> 00:23:27,864
[Edward] <i>I said, shut up!</i>

464
00:23:27,948 --> 00:23:30,158
- [sobbing continues]
<i>- Shut up!</i>

465
00:23:30,492 --> 00:23:31,701
[thunder claps]

466
00:23:31,785 --> 00:23:33,745
[girl] <i>Help me!</i>

467
00:23:33,829 --> 00:23:35,455
<i>Help!</i>

468
00:23:35,539 --> 00:23:37,874
- [Edward] <i>Shut up!</i>
- [girl] <i>Mama!</i>

469
00:23:37,958 --> 00:23:39,543
[Edward] <i>Goddammit! Shut up!</i>

470
00:23:39,626 --> 00:23:40,710
<i>Shut up!</i>

471
00:23:40,794 --> 00:23:45,048
- [girl sobbing]
- [music becomes ominous]

472
00:23:45,841 --> 00:23:47,592
[girl on video] <i>Help me!</i>

473
00:23:52,389 --> 00:23:54,766
- [Edward]<i> Shut up!</i>
- [girl cries] <i>Have mercy on me!</i>

474
00:23:54,850 --> 00:23:56,560
<i>- Shut up!</i>
- [sobs]

475
00:23:56,643 --> 00:23:57,602
[Edward] <i>Goddammit!</i>
<i>Why won't you shut up?!</i>

476
00:23:57,686 --> 00:23:59,062
[girl]<i> Don't hurt me!</i>

477
00:23:59,146 --> 00:24:00,105
[Edward] <i>Shut up!</i>

478
00:24:00,188 --> 00:24:01,857
[girl] <i>Help me!</i>

479
00:24:01,940 --> 00:24:07,279
[ominous music continues]

480
00:24:10,115 --> 00:24:12,534
[footsteps receding]

481
00:24:12,617 --> 00:24:17,747
[ominous music continues]

482
00:24:22,335 --> 00:24:23,837
- [Louisa gasps]
<i>- Louisa?</i>

483
00:24:24,254 --> 00:24:26,131
[dramatic music sting]

484
00:24:27,966 --> 00:24:31,845
<i>Finally, it is all complete.</i>

485
00:24:32,220 --> 00:24:34,389
<i>Who should I kill first?</i>

486
00:24:34,472 --> 00:24:36,641
<i>Edong, forgive us! Please, forgive me!</i>

487
00:24:36,725 --> 00:24:38,935
- [Edong laughs]
<i>- It's not your fault!</i>

488
00:24:39,019 --> 00:24:42,689
<i>- It's my fault!</i>
<i>- I don't need your apology.</i>

489
00:24:42,772 --> 00:24:44,065
<i>You destroyed our lives!</i>

490
00:24:44,149 --> 00:24:46,443
<i>You destroyed our family!</i>

491
00:24:46,526 --> 00:24:48,486
<i>Put the gun down! Put it down!</i>

492
00:24:48,570 --> 00:24:49,404
<i>Edong…</i>

493
00:24:49,487 --> 00:24:50,947
<i>You would shoot your own brother?</i>

494
00:24:51,031 --> 00:24:52,782
<i>Don't make me, Edong.</i>

495
00:24:52,866 --> 00:24:55,410
[both grunting]

496
00:24:55,493 --> 00:24:56,494
- [gunshots]
- [screams]
